==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Muntjac
<hw>Munt"jac</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of small Asiatic deer of the genus
<gen>Cervulus</gen>, esp. <spn>Cervulus muntjac</spn>, which occurs both
in India and on the East Indian Islands.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>muntjak</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

